'''Batangafo Airport''' {{Airport codes|BTG|FEGF}} is an airport serving [[Batangafo]], a city on the [[Ouham River]] in the [[Ouham]] prefecture of the [[Central African Republic]]. The airport is on the northeastern edge of the city, just off the RN4 road.
