A '''travel warning''', '''travel alert''', or '''travel advisory''' is an official [[Precautionary statement|warning statement]] issued by a [[government agency]] to provide information about the relative safety of [[travel]]ling to or visiting one or more specific foreign [[country|countries]] or destinations.<ref>{{cite web|title=Travel warning definition |url=http://www.macmillandictionary.com/dictionary/british/travel-warning|publisher=Macmillan Publishers|accessdate=11 February 2013}}</ref> The purpose is to enable travelers to make an informed decision about a particular travel destination, and to help travellers prepare adequately for what may be encountered on their trip. In the [[United States]], travel warnings are issued by the [[United States Department of State|Department of State]] and are often called warden messages.<ref name="USDoS">{{cite web|title=Alerts and Warnings|url=https://travel.state.gov/content/passports/english/alertswarnings.html|publisher=[[United States Department of State]]|accessdate=22 August 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://burma.usembassy.gov/warden_messages.html|title=Emergency Messages and Announcements - Rangoon, Burma - Embassy of the United States|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref>
Travel advisories may relate to issues such as [[inclement weather]], [[security]] matters, [[civil unrest]] or [[disease]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Travel Alerts|url=http://www.smilex.cz/cestovni-vystrahy#warnings|publisher=Agentura SMILEX|accessdate=11 February 2013|language=Czech}}</ref>
==Countries issuing warnings== {{expand list|date=August 2015}} The following countries regularly publish travel warnings to their citizens: *[[Australia]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smartraveller.gov.au/|title=Smartraveller|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref> *[[Austria]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bmeia.gv.at/aussenministerium/buergerservice/reiseinformation/laenderspezifische-reiseinformationen.html|title=Länder A bis Z – BMEIA, Außenministerium Österreich|author=Außenministerium der Republik Österreich|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}{{Dead link|date=July 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref> *[[Belgium]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://diplomatie.belgium.be/fr/Services/voyager_a_letranger/conseils_par_destination/|title=Services - Page d’accueil - Affaires étrangères, Commerce extérieur et Coopération au Développement|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref> *[[Bulgaria]]<ref>[http://www.mfa.bg/uploads/files/Documents/StatesRisk02072013.pdf СТЕПЕНИ НА СИГУРНОСТ ПРЕПОРЪКИ И ПРЕДУПРЕЖДЕНИЯ ЗА ПЪТУВАНЕ]</ref> *[[Canada]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://travel.gc.ca/|title=Travel.gc.ca - Home|work=Travel.gc.ca|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://voyage.gc.ca/|title=Voyage.gc.ca - Accueil|work=Voyage.gc.ca|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref> *[[Croatia]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mvep.hr/hr/konzularne-informacije/informacije-o-putovanjima/opce-informacije/|title=MVEP • Opće informacije|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref> *[[Cyprus]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mfa.gov.cy/mfa/mfa2006.nsf/travel.html|title=Ταξιδιωτικές Οδηγίες|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref> *[[Czech Republic]]<ref>[http://www.mzv.cz/jnp/cz/cestujeme/aktualni_doporuceni_a_varovani/index.html Aktuální doporučení a varování]</ref> *[[Denmark]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://um.dk/da/rejse-og-ophold/rejse-til-udlandet/rejsevejledninger/|title=Rejsevejledninger|publisher=|accessdate=30 January 2016}}</ref> *[[Estonia]]<ref>